Police operatives attached to Alakuko station with the help of some communities yesterday arrested four suspected armed robbers at midnight. The suspects were said to have been terrorising and dispossessing residents of Ajegunle, Masalasi, and Dalemo communities in Alakuko area of Lagos State, of their belongings.
Â 
